Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Located at 205 Blackmarsh Road, this 2403 sf retail space is available for lease. Landlord is receptive to demising into 2 x 1200 sf units. Tenant mix includes long standing restaurant business and tax business. Surrounded by a heavy residential area and retail nodes close by including Ropewalk Lane and Columbus Drive. Easy access from Gushue extension. Ample parking onsite. Lease rate is $14.75 plus $7.50 operating costs and tenant paying own utilities.

Located on Kenmount Road at the intersection of Kelsey Drive. Three units available with a total of 6,040 SF. Rental rate is $27.00 per square foot and operating costs are $10.00 per square foot. Potential for further development on property. Unit 2 - 2170 SF Unit 3 - 1820 SF Unit 4 - 2050 SF

Brand new building in the bustling Kenmount/Kelsey Drive area. Neighbouring Kenmount Terrace with hundreds of rooftops, seconds away from the Team Gushue Highway and next to Kelsey Drive; Kiwanis Street is a wonderful location for a number of businesses.Great plaza with exceptional curb appeal for professional offices, services and health and wellness. Each unit has a basement which is excellent for storage. Units can be combined for larger space.
